            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "施壓升級 美國司法部對聯儲會庫克啟動刑事調查",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 美國司法部對聯儲會理事麗莎·庫克是否涉及抵押貸款欺詐啟動刑事調查，在總統唐納德·川普尋求將她免職之際加大施壓。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">因討論未公開消息而要求匿名的知情人士表示，聯邦檢察官已發出傳票，要求提供與庫克在抵押貸款申請中涉嫌虛假陳述相關的信息。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">在聯邦住房金融局局長Bill Pulte指控庫克在密西根州和喬治亞州的房產涉及抵押貸款欺詐後，川普上月表示將免去庫克的職務。庫克已起訴政府要求繼續履職，她的律師稱總統缺乏正當理由將其免職。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">司法部和庫克的律師均未立即回應置評請求。《華爾街日報》周四早些時候報導了司法部的調查。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Justice Department Opens Criminal Probe of Lisa Cook Mortgages</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2025 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%96%BD%E5%A3%93%E5%8D%87%E7%B4%9A-%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E5%8F%B8%E6%B3%95%E9%83%A8%E5%B0%8D%E8%81%AF%E5%84%B2%E6%9C%83%E5%BA%AB%E5%85%8B%E5%95%9F%E5%8B%95%E5%88%91%E4%BA%8B%E8%AA%BF%E6%9F%A5-153338307.html",
            "pub_date": "2025-09-05 00:30:45",
