        },
        {
            "title": "美國國債殖利率跌至數月最低 更多就業數據為降息提供支撐",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"540\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/BdoWbfqHWT9GIAXd2oZ7ww--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU0MDtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/89d10735eb395af369384f9969bb7ba6\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 多項基準美國國債殖利率跌至數月來最低水平，因更多勞動力市場降溫跡象強化了市場對聯儲會本月開始降息的預期。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">各期限殖利率僅小幅下降，但5年期殖利率觸及自4月初美國政府關稅計畫引發債市反彈以來的最低點，10年期國債殖利率跌破4.17%，至5月初以來最低水平。</p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\" \" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"540\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/wq7KZyeNGb4hzUp0BuNzXg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU0MDtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/f76d6a6cd1282608998368a07714818b\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\"> </figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">周四公佈的反映私營行業招聘情況的ADP報告低於預期，而勞工部的單周失業救濟申請人數超過經濟學家的預測。勞工部將於周五發布8月份非農就業報告，預計將確認7月數據中的招聘放緩趨勢，並顯示失業率升至4.3%，為2021年以來最高水平。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Mischler Financial Group董事總經理Tom di Galoma表示：「聯儲會無疑會在9月降息」，年底前以及明年可能還會進一步下調利率。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">利率合約定價顯示，本月降息25個基點的概率約為90%，預計年底前至少再降兩次。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Treasury Yields Lowest in Months as Jobs Data Back Rate Cuts</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">--聯合報導 Ye Xie、Edward Bolingbroke.</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2025 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E5%9C%8B%E5%82%B5%E6%AE%96%E5%88%A9%E7%8E%87%E8%B7%8C%E8%87%B3%E6%95%B8%E6%9C%88%E6%9C%80%E4%BD%8E-%E6%9B%B4%E5%A4%9A%E5%B0%B1%E6%A5%AD%E6%95%B8%E6%93%9A%E7%82%BA%E9%99%8D%E6%81%AF%E6%8F%90%E4%BE%9B%E6%94%AF%E6%92%90-145254745.html",
            "pub_date": "2025-09-04 23:25:42",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "馬克龍稱26個國家將支持對烏克蘭的安全保障",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 法國總統埃馬紐埃爾·<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-ylk=\"slk:馬克龍;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/馬克龍\">馬克龍</a>稱，已有26個國家承諾在俄烏停火的情況下向<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-ylk=\"slk:烏克蘭;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/烏克蘭\">烏克蘭</a>提供安全保障，唐納德·川普未給出美國將予以支持的承諾。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">馬克龍在巴黎與烏克蘭總統沃洛迪米爾·澤連斯基一同舉行記者會時稱，美國對於安全保障的支持將在幾天內確定，該支持旨在防止烏克蘭受到俄羅斯的進一步襲擊。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">馬克龍周四與所謂的「自願聯盟」國家舉行了會議，匯集了歐洲領導人，他們準備向停火後的烏克蘭提供保障，其中包括可能的軍隊部署。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Macron Says 26 Nations to Back Security Guarantees for Ukraine</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2025 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E9%A6%AC%E5%85%8B%E9%BE%8D%E7%A8%B126%E5%80%8B%E5%9C%8B%E5%AE%B6%E5%B0%87%E6%94%AF%E6%8C%81%E5%B0%8D%E7%83%8F%E5%85%8B%E8%98%AD%E7%9A%84%E5%AE%89%E5%85%A8%E4%BF%9D%E9%9A%9C-151456512.html",
            "pub_date": "2025-09-05 00:30:47",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "美國7月貿易逆差擴大至四個月新高 企業在川普新關稅前集中進口",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 美國7月貿易逆差擴大至四個月高點，企業爭相在總統唐納德·川普對全球貿易夥伴加徵新關稅前進口商品和原物料。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">美國商務部周四公佈的數據顯示，當月商品和服務貿易逆差較之前一個月擴大近33%，達到783億美元。此前彭博對經濟學家的調查中值顯示，逆差規模料為約780億美元。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">進口額在連續三個月下滑後，7月成長5.9%，出口小幅上升。數據未經通膨調整。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">進口的激增主要源於工業用品進口量攀升至四個月高點。消費品進口同樣成長，而除汽車外的資本設備進口增幅創下年初以來新高。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">該報告顯示，美國企業爭相在未與美國達成貿易協議的國家正式受到對等關稅影響之前，囤積更多商品。此前受企業搶在4月2日關稅前囤貨影響，一季度進口大幅成長，但此後連續三個月下滑。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">今年貿易數據的劇烈月度波動，也導致政府衡量經濟活動的指標 —— 國內生產毛額(GDP) —— 呈現類似的波動。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題US Trade Gap Widens to Largest in Four Months on Import Flurry</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">--聯合報導 Michael Sasso.</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">(新增文末三段內容)</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2025 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B7%E6%9C%88%E8%B2%BF%E6%98%93%E9%80%86%E5%B7%AE%E6%93%B4%E5%A4%A7%E8%87%B3%E5%9B%9B%E5%80%8B%E6%9C%88%E6%96%B0%E9%AB%98-%E4%BC%81%E6%A5%AD%E5%9C%A8%E5%B7%9D%E6%99%AE%E6%96%B0%E9%97%9C%E7%A8%85%E5%89%8D%E9%9B%86%E4%B8%AD%E9%80%B2%E5%8F%A3-130020853.html",
            "pub_date": "2025-09-04 21:35:42",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "美國服務業擴張速度達到六個月來最快 訂單指標大幅成長",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 8月份美國服務業活動以六個月來最快速度擴張，訂單增幅達到近一年以來最大。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">供應管理學會(ISM)周四公佈的數據顯示，服務業指數上月上升1.9點至52，超過了彭博調查的幾乎所有經濟學家的預估。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">新訂單指標跳升5.7點至56，為去年9月以來最大升幅。商業活動指數指標升至五個月高點55。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">這些指標表明占美國經濟最大比重的服務業在連續五個月疲軟之後正獲得一些動力。與此同時，材料成本指標顯示，服務提供商仍在與通膨作鬥爭。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">雖然價格支付指標有所回落，但8月讀數為69.2，是自2022年底以來的次高水平，顯示出關稅的影響。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">報告的其他細節喜憂參半。訂單積壓指標降至2009年以來最低，這也解釋了為何服務提供商在擴充人手方面並不急切。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">ISM就業指標幾乎沒有變化，連續第三個月處於收縮區間，也是自疫情以來最弱水平之一。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題US Services Activity Expands at Fastest Pace in Six Months</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2025 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E6%9C%8D%E5%8B%99%E6%A5%AD%E6%93%B4%E5%BC%B5%E9%80%9F%E5%BA%A6%E9%81%94%E5%88%B0%E5%85%AD%E5%80%8B%E6%9C%88%E4%BE%86%E6%9C%80%E5%BF%AB-%E8%A8%82%E5%96%AE%E6%8C%87%E6%A8%99%E5%A4%A7%E5%B9%85%E6%88%90%E9%95%B7-141509784.html",
